00:06:29.160 --> 00:06:33.040
so this is lower limb to upper limb. You
can pretty much pick your favorite

00:06:33.040 --> 00:06:37.100
measure, it doesn't much matter. And you
can see that chimps and gorillas here have

00:06:37.100 --> 00:06:41.450
