00:07:14.090 --> 00:07:18.820
flexible, so it can wrap around branches
and hang on in the trees. Whereas our feet

00:07:18.820 --> 00:07:22.330
are very stiff and they form a nice
propulsive lever to move us forward when

00:07:22.330 --> 00:07:25.900
we walk on the ground on two feet, and
that propulsive lever is supported by

00:07:25.900 --> 00:07:29.880
arches that go from front to back and side
to side that are built into the structure

00:07:29.880 --> 00:07:33.690
of the bones of our foot. So one we lift
our heels off the ground, they stiffen up

00:07:33.690 --> 00:07:38.620
and they let us work well. We've known for
